Title: Some Wicked Things This Way Come
Description:
Phineas did well in bringing you to me, $p. There is much work to be done.

We'd best get to it!

As a master of the dark arts, I need you to help me whip these newcomers into shape. Talk to them. They come from many walks of life--all of them unfamiliar with the dark arts.

Learn their wishes. 

Their hopes.

Their dreams.

This path we walk can bestow gifts unending and power unimaginable. One just needs to know what one truly desires...
ObjectivesText: Talk to the newly arrived warlocks around the Darkmoon Faire.
RewardText:
Only one or two pairs of cold feet, hm? 

<Madam Shadow chuckles.>

Excellent.

Now that we know who wants to be here, it is time to determine who deserves to be here.
